	<title>Development setup</title>
	
	<para>
	In short, the following steps have to be performed:
	
	<itemizedlist>
	
    <listitem><para>Install Eclipse 4.4 (Luna)</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Clone <link xlink:href="https://github.com/ctron/package-drone"/></para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Import all projects using Eclipse Git</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Run <code>ant -f build.ant</code> in project runtime</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Open the file <filename>runtime/runtime.target</filename></para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Press <guimenuitem>Set as target platform</guimenuitem> (upper right corner)</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Launch <guimenuitem>Jetty</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Run Configurations</guimenu> menu</para></listitem>
	
	</itemizedlist>
	
	</para>
		
